RACE.RACE_TEXT: PRAIRIE MEADOWS RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 76. Claiming Purse 14100. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON TWO RACES SINCE DECEMBER 10, 2022. RACE.FOOTNOTES: DIXIE PENNY sat back in the opening quarter then crept up three wide to engage rivals midway around the turn, got carried out wide heading into the stretch run, dueled with JAZZ BRUNCH down the lane, dug in under firm handling and edged away. JAZZ BRUNCH raced three wide just off the top pair up the backstretch, moved up to challenge for the lead with three furlongs left to run, dueled around the turn, drifted out heading into upper stretch, battled on with DIXIE PENNY into final stages and got denied nearing the wire. CHAMPAGNE BLING settled off the pace up the backstretch then urged to picked up the tempo mid-way around the turn, was forced to go wide heading into the lane, came back in a couple paths, sustained bid and cleared show. BOLD LEGEND tracked the pace along the inside, cut the corner entering the stretch run, moved up into strong contention at the eighth pole but failed to sustain bid. GLAMOROUS LIFE was off a step slow at the start and continued in the back, hustled along three wide into the lane and lacked a needed rally. NOSTALGIA set a pressured pace up the backstretch, dueled around the turn, battled back into upper stretch then gave way. UNHERDOF pressed the early pace, dueled late on the backstretch, weakened mid-way around the turn and continued to tire in the drive.
